name: Techno King #101
description: This image features a powerful figure, embodying both the raw energy of nature and the intelligence of technology. The character's skin is a blend of earthy textures, glowing with lines of neon-like circuits and symbols. They wear a crown of leaves, signifying their dominion over both the organic and the digital. A parrot perches on their shoulder, adding a natural, regal touch. Their attire includes armor adorned with various organic elements, intertwining the primitive and the technological.

attributes.value: Crown of leaves, parrot on shoulder
